<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٠١٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/461">أَحْمَدُ بْنُ يُونُسَ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5348">اللَّيْثُ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٍ: </a>أَنَّ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">عَبْدَ اللهِ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> أَخْبَرَهُ: <span class="c2">«أَنَّ امْرَأَةً وُجِدَتْ فِي بَعْضِ مَغَازِي النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> مَقْتُولَةً فَأَنْكَرَ رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَتْلَ النِّسَاءِ وَالصِّبْيَانِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>